data.description: Do You Have A Large Down Payment But Need A LOW Rate Assumable Mortgage? This Alpharetta Home Is Your Next Home! Beautiful Traditional Brick Home In One Of The Most Sought-After Areas To Live North Of Atlanta. "MILTON" Has It All Awaiting Your Family In This Beautifully Appointed, Spacious Alpharetta Home. TOP Schools, Dining And Area Amenities Are Matchless. Walk In The Front Door And Experience The Rare Curvature Foyer With Stunning Staircase Opening To Living, Dining And Family Rooms.  The Family Room Is Complete With A Fireplace, Built-In Bookcases And A Wet Bar! The Main Floor Features Beautifully Refinished Hardwood Floors And New, Maintenance-Free Luxury Vinyl Plank (LVP) Completing The Rest Of The Home. The Oversized Sunroom With Skylights Can Be Used As An Office Giving You Focused Scenery Of A Private Back Yard Or Put In A Hammock Or Daybed To Enjoy Nature And All The Natural Light.  Don't Miss Relaxing On The HUGE Screen Porch With Teak Wood Mat Flooring To Enjoy The Private Views With Available Gardening.  Entertain In This Completely Renovated Kitchen Featuring New Cabinets, Granite Countertops, Center Island Cooktop, Updated Lighting And All Stainless Appliances.  Retreat For Rest And Relaxation In The Oversized Owner's Suite With His & Her Closets (Updated To California Style Shelving) And Separate Shower/Spa Bathtub. Three Additional Bedrooms Share A Nice Size Double Vanity, Hall Bathroom.  The 4th Bedroom Can Also Function As A Huge Bonus Room With Its Built-In Bookcases And Back Stairs That Take You To The Kitchen.  That Is A Rare Feature You Will Absolutely Love And Use. Don't Miss The Unfinished Basement And Two-Car Side-Entry Garage! The Basement Could Be Easily Finished (Electrical Already In Place) For More Rooms Or Just Use It As Conditioned Space For A Workshop Or A Rec/Workout Area.  This Home Has What You Are Looking For.....Close To Everything You Want To Do, See And With Easy Access To 400, Avalon, Parks, And The Downtown Alpharetta & Roswell Hot Spots.
